data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Completed in June of 2023! Nestled amidst the scenic beauty of a water-view homesite lies the near-pristine Contour Floorplan, a masterpiece by Del Webb. Showcasing a Florida Mediterranean exterior, this single-story gem is just a stone’s throw away from the amenity center. Step inside to unveil a tapestry of luxury: 2 spacious bedrooms, two pristine bathrooms, and an enclosed flex room tailored for office tasks or extra bedroom. A generous 2-car garage, ample storage, and an oversized kitchen that seamlessly melds with a gathering room await. Step onto the extended patio and let the shimmering pond embrace your senses, simplifying indoor-outdoor festivities. Your culinary aspirations will thrive in the gourmet kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances, a spacious island, pendant lighting provisions, a 42” Stone Gray Lillian soft-close cabinet ensemble, an elegant white picket tile backsplash, and stunning Lagoon quartz countertops. Revel in the tranquility of the Owner's Suite, where an en suite bathroom boasts a Blanco Maple quartz-topped double Stone Gray vanity, a walk-in glass shower, and a private lavatory flanked by a linen closet and a walk-in wardrobe. The juxtaposition of the secondary bedroom, bathroom, flex room, and enhanced laundry section ensures privacy and ample space. Del Webb Sunbridge—a gated haven for the 55+ community, premiering in the Sunbridge Masterplan. Experience a lifestyle upgrade in this natural gas community that promotes ease with new construction homes and a low-maintenance lifestyle nestled in Central Florida's heart. The 27,000-square foot clubhouse pulsates with activities orchestrated by a dedicated Lifestyle Director. Dive into relaxation with a zero-entry pool, feel the warmth at the heated spa, or swing into action with sports courts and walking trails. From art studios, amphitheaters, the Sabal tavern & grille to fire pits, every corner promises memories. Relax, for this is YOUR time. With exterior and yard upkeep handled, tap into Gigabit-speed internet via the fiber network. Experience unparalleled amenities, sports courts, and the guidance of a Lifestyle Director. Close to Lake Nona.
